<p>You can now use <a href="/datasync/">AWS DataSync</a> for workloads that are subject to Service Organization Control (SOC) compliance. DataSync is an online data transfer service that simplifies, automates, and accelerates copying data between NFS file servers, Amazon S3 buckets, and Amazon Elastic File System (EFS) file systems using a purpose-built network protocol to achieve speeds of up to 10x faster than open source tools.</p>